---
layout: base
eleventyNavigation:
    key: Home
    order: 1
---

<div class="container">

    <h1 class="main-title">
        <span>Welcome!</span>
        {#- <span class="size-adjust">Welcome!</span> -#}
    </h1>
    <div class="post">
        <h2 style="font-size: var(--fluid-1);font-family: var(--sub-sans)">
            My name is {% serifName %} and this is my blog where I post thoughts, tutorials, <del>rants</del> opinions, and just general blog posts.
        </h2>
        <br/>
        <div class="post-grid">
            <h3 class="post-grid-title" style="font-size: var(--fluid-1);">Here's some posts that I think you should check out!</h3>
            {% set numberOfFeaturedPosts = 0 %}
            {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
                {% if post.data.featured and numberOfFeaturedPosts < 2%}
                    {% set numberOfFeaturedPosts = numberOfFeaturedPosts + 1 %}
                    {% include 'post.njk' %}
                {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>